metadata.name: Axolittle #1
metadata.description: Axolittles is a collection of 10,000 algorithmically generated pieces of art, assembled from over 160 traits. They're inspired by axolotls, the world's cutest amphibians. Each Axolittle is animated and comes with a 48-frame GIF that loops perfectly so you could stare at it for hours!
